comments: Randle (NYK) places a forearm to the front of Hayward (BOS) and the contact affects his SQBR.
Morris (NYK) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Tatum's (BOS) drive to the basket at shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) makes contact with Barrett (NYK) that affects his SQBR.
Hayward (BOS) is in a legal guarding position when Morris Sr. (NYK) leans forward and the two players inadvertently make head contact.
Tatum (BOS) makes contact with Randle's (NYK) arm that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ntilikina (NYK) and does not deliver contact.
Barrett (NYK) makes contact with Smart's (BOS) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Walker (BOS) and Ellington (NYK) engage and disengage off ball.
Randle (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in Tatum's (BOS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Tatum (BOS) makes contact to Morris Sr.'s (NYK) arm after the release that affects his jump shot attempt.
Theis (BOS) clamps Randle's (NYK) arm and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Theis (BOS) and Morris Sr. (NYK) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Smart (BOS) and Ellington (NYK) engage and disengage off ball.
During the screen, Tatum (BOS) makes contact with Morris Sr. (NYK) that affects his FOM.
Knox II (NYK) commits a take foul on Walker (BOS).
Walker (BOS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Barrett's (NYK) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) makes marginal contact with Barrett (NYK) off ball that does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
